00:05:59.193 --> 00:06:00.861 position:50% align:center
[AI]
Mm.

00:06:00.944 --> 00:06:02.196 position:50% align:center
[OTHER AI]
That's cool.

00:06:02.279 --> 00:06:04.072 position:50% align:center
You actually made a friend.

00:06:04.156 --> 00:06:04.948 position:50% align:center
