00:06:40.692 --> 00:06:42.986 position:50% align:center
They're after you.

00:06:43.070 --> 00:06:44.655 position:50% align:center
But I'll protect you.

00:06:44.738 --> 00:06:46.990 position:50% align:center
I'll keep you safe.

00:06:47.074 --> 00:06:48.534 position:50% align:center
