00:06:50.118 --> 00:06:51.870 position:50% align:center
I promise.

00:06:51.954 --> 00:06:54.915 position:50% align:center
'Cause I've gotten stronger.

00:06:54.998 --> 00:06:56.667 position:50% align:center
