Ai? Ai!

00:07:59.897 --> 00:08:01.315 position:50% align:center
Ai?

00:08:05.527 --> 00:08:07.196 position:50% align:center
You okay?

00:08:16.955 --> 00:08:18.707 position:50% align:center
[OTHER AI]
About Koito.

00:08:18.790 --> 00:08:21.168 position:50% align:center
