00:08:37.726 --> 00:08:39.686 position:50% align:center
She's a mystery.

00:08:44.441 --> 00:08:47.736 position:50% align:center
[MONSTER SAWAKI laughs]

00:08:47.819 --> 00:08:49.196 position:50% align:center
[BOTH AIS]
Mister Sawaki?

00:08:49.279 --> 00:08:53.784 position:50% align:center
Yes. I'm your sweet
mother's fiancÃ©.

00:09:09.633 --> 00:09:10.634 position:50% align:center
