00:16:39.791 --> 00:16:41.084 position:50% align:center
Ai!

00:16:41.710 --> 00:16:45.422 position:50% align:center
[AI] I'm done with the old me
that just wanted attention.

00:16:45.506 --> 00:16:46.965 position:50% align:center
