[OTHER AI]
That's great, other me!

00:17:45.983 --> 00:17:47.568 position:50% align:center
I'm glad for you.

00:17:52.322 --> 00:17:54.157 position:50% align:center
You can see her again soon.

00:17:55.868 --> 00:17:56.869 position:50% align:center
[AI]
The thing is,

00:17:56.952 --> 00:17:57.953 position:50% align:center
I thought I wanted
to hear the truth

00:17:58.036 --> 00:18:00.122 position:50% align:center
from Koito about her suicide.

00:18:00.205 --> 00:18:01.623 position:50% align:center
Now, I dunno.

00:18:01.707 --> 00:18:03.333 position:50% align:center
Oh, really?

00:18:03.417 --> 00:18:04.668 position:50% align:center
[AI]
Mm.

00:18:04.751 --> 00:18:07.588 position:50% align:center
But... I think
I just feel grateful.

00:18:07.671 --> 00:18:09.798 position:50% align:center
Even if it was a lie?

00:18:09.882 --> 00:18:11.341 position:50% align:center
Yeah, maybe.

00:18:11.425 --> 00:18:13.677 position:50% align:center
Koito really saved me back then.

00:18:13.760 --> 00:18:16.930 position:50% align:center
I wasn't alone anymore.

00:18:17.014 --> 00:18:18.432 position:50% align:center
That's it.

00:18:18.515 --> 00:18:19.600 position:50% align:center
What is?

00:18:19.683 --> 00:18:23.770 position:50% align:center
I've decided to become
a Warrior of Eros.

00:18:23.854 --> 00:18:26.899 position:50% align:center
