the temptation of death.

00:18:26.982 --> 00:18:30.277 position:50% align:center
And I may not know how to go
to parallel worlds just yet,

00:18:30.360 --> 00:18:33.197 position:50% align:center
but someday,
I promise to bring you back.

00:18:33.280 --> 00:18:36.575 position:50% align:center
Because... I'm sure
your mom must be sad.

00:18:36.658 --> 00:18:39.745 position:50% align:center
In that case, I want to try
and get strong like you are.

00:18:41.413 --> 00:18:42.539 position:50% align:center
Don't be silly.

00:18:42.623 --> 00:18:45.083 position:50% align:center
Me and you are the same person.

00:18:45.167 --> 00:18:46.752 position:50% align:center
Oh, true.

00:18:46.835 --> 00:18:49.546 position:50% align:center
Can't really argue with that!

00:18:49.630 --> 00:18:51.757 position:50% align:center
I'll see you again.

00:18:51.840 --> 00:18:52.799 position:50% align:center
Okay, Ai.

00:18:52.883 --> 00:18:54.426 position:50% align:center
I'll be waiting.

00:18:54.510 --> 00:18:56.136 position:50% align:center
[KIRARA]
Ha. Ha.

00:18:57.179 --> 00:18:59.056 position:50% align:center
Ha.

00:18:59.139 --> 00:19:00.140 position:50% align:center
Ha, ha.

00:19:00.224 --> 00:19:01.767 position:50% align:center
[AI]
<i>Redi.</i>

00:19:01.850 --> 00:19:03.310 position:50% align:center
[KIRARA]
Hello.

00:19:03.393 --> 00:19:07.856 position:50% align:center
