Eighteen Evening Star SS Plum.

00:19:07.940 --> 00:19:10.817 position:50% align:center
Kirara... Whatty what?

00:19:24.331 --> 00:19:26.124 position:50% align:center
[RIKA]
What the...?

00:19:26.208 --> 00:19:27.918 position:50% align:center
What's going on?
Let me in, you bastards!

00:19:28.001 --> 00:19:30.003 position:50% align:center
Ura-Acca.

00:19:30.087 --> 00:19:32.506 position:50% align:center
There's no need,
her mission is over.

00:19:32.589 --> 00:19:35.300 position:50% align:center
[RIKA] Let me in, I wanna
get even for Mannen!

00:19:35.384 --> 00:19:38.095 position:50% align:center
