certain unless we try, though.

00:19:40.973 --> 00:19:43.267 position:50% align:center
Come now, don't you care
what happens to that girl?

00:19:43.350 --> 00:19:45.936 position:50% align:center
She's aware of the risk.

00:19:46.019 --> 00:19:47.813 position:50% align:center
I'm starting to think that
you don't actually care

00:19:47.896 --> 00:19:50.941 position:50% align:center
