want to do is save Himari.

00:19:56.864 --> 00:19:59.449 position:50% align:center
Perhaps. Ura-Acca.

00:19:59.533 --> 00:20:02.536 position:50% align:center
Then again, isn't that
how we've always been?

00:20:06.164 --> 00:20:07.833 position:50% align:center
[KIRARA]
I won't kill you.

00:20:07.916 --> 00:20:09.543 position:50% align:center
I won't.

00:20:21.430 --> 00:20:23.807 position:50% align:center
It's so shiny.

00:20:31.523 --> 00:20:33.108 position:50% align:center
It was the other me.

00:20:33.192 --> 00:20:35.277 position:50% align:center
Wasn't it?

00:20:35.360 --> 00:20:37.070 position:50% align:center
She saved me.

00:20:37.154 --> 00:20:39.031 position:50% align:center
Protected me.

00:20:42.618 --> 00:20:44.411 position:50% align:center
Ai!

00:20:47.414 --> 00:20:48.707 position:50% align:center
[KIRARA]
I want them.

00:20:48.790 --> 00:20:50.000 position:50% align:center
Shiny things.

00:20:50.083 --> 00:20:52.127 position:50% align:center
Shiny things?

00:20:57.841 --> 00:20:59.843 position:50% align:center
[OTHER AI]
We're the same.

00:21:08.560 --> 00:21:11.104 position:50% align:center
Take care. Me.

00:21:14.191 --> 00:21:16.068 position:50% align:center
I'm sorry.

00:21:23.617 --> 00:21:25.369 position:50% align:center
[BOTH AIS]
Thank you, Ai.

00:22:58.629 --> 00:23:00.464 position:50% align:center
[AI]
Thank you so much.